## 21st United States National Census

The twenty-first decennial census of the [United States](/United_States), officially designated as the [1990 United States census](/1990_United_States_census), was conducted by the [Census Bureau](/United_States_Census_Bureau). It was a monumental, if rather tiresome, undertaking that aimed to count every single resident within the nation's borders.

